    <mxCell id="t032A6oZSB83beidUFNQ-43" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;rounded=0;" value="&lt;div align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Description&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div align=&quot;left&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,0,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;This UML class diagram illustrates the static structure of a clinic management system, covering the entire workflow from booking to prescription fulfillment.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,1,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;The &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Patient&lt;/b&gt; class acts as the service initiator, maintaining a one-to-many [&lt;span class=&quot;math-inline&quot; data-math=&quot;1:*&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;76&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;1:*]&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;relationship with the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;103&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Appointment&lt;/b&gt; class.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;The &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Clinic&lt;/b&gt; class serves as the administrative authority, managing available slots and coordinating the scheduling of all &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;121&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Appointments&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,3,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;A &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;2&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Doctor&lt;/b&gt; class is included, representing medical staff who hold a one-to-many [&lt;span class=&quot;math-inline&quot; data-math=&quot;1:n&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;79&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;1:n]&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;relationship with the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;106&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Clinic&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Every &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;6&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Appointment&lt;/b&gt; is assigned to a specific doctor and eventually results in a single &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;86&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Consultation&lt;/b&gt; session.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;During the &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;11&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Consultation&lt;/b&gt;, the doctor records key &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;48&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;diagnosis&lt;/code&gt; details and &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;70&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;examNotes&lt;/code&gt; by executing the &lt;code data-path-to-node=&quot;1,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;97&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;conductExam()&lt;/code&gt; method.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;The &lt;span class=&quot;math-inline&quot; data-math=&quot;0..1&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;[0..1]&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;multiplicity between &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;30&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;Consultation&lt;/b&gt; and &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,6,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;47&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;MedicationOrder&lt;/b&gt; accurately reflects that a prescription is an optional outcome of a diagnosis.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,0&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-height: 1.15 !important; margin-top: 0px !important;&quot;&gt;The &lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;1,7,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;4&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Google Sans Text, sans-serif !important; line-heig